name: Deep Cyan
description:
“Deep Cyan” is third and last subsets of Crystal Ninja, those atmosphere is affected by distortion and the change of background color drop threshold. 
This video artwork has random distortion
each of them has unique background color drop threshold percentage and hexadecimal color code.
The effect on this artwork is influenced by the nightmare that the creator had on the first night of his Covid-19 illness.
Cdt%: 63.9%
Hex color code : #6688a3
